$$ {P}_{\mathrm{TP}}={P}_{\mathrm{ALV}}-{P}_{\mathrm{PL}}. $$
\end{document}PTP=PALV−PPL.Unfortunately, neither P
ALV nor P
PL can be directly measured, but they are reasonably estimated by P
PLAT and esophageal pressure (P
ESO), respectively [38]. Hence:24.8\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
